Tight-binding calculation of an infinite spin chain on a 1-D superconductor
###########
To calculate band structure and topological invariant run:
python BCS_infinite_chain_k_space.py
#
Parameters: param_phase_diag.py
##########
To obtain the topological phase diagram run:
python PhaseDiag_chain_k_space_JS_mu_.py
#
Parameters: param_inf.py
#########
To calculate the finite spin chain run:
python Run_BCS_chain_k_space.py
#
Parameters: param.py
